description: JMC is the equity token of Jemoo ecology and undertakes the important responsibilities of ecological construction, user motivation and value circulation of Jemoo. Jemoo expects to build a  fair, transparent, efficient and collaborative social platform of valuable content which fulfills community governing and integrates the blockchain system, so as to truly focus on users, let the attention of content producers and consumers return to content production itself, and achieve decent creation and valuable social intercourse.
